                            <ptr target="bib:ARIE1939-1943"/> (standardised): <quote>Begins with the historical introduction <foreign>samastajagadādhāra</foreign>, etc. Records a royal order making a tax-free <foreign>dēvadāna</foreign> endowment of the village Nallūr to the temple of Nalla-Nāyaṉār for the maintenance of a service in the name of the king and for the (expenses of the) festival in the month of Tai.</quote>
                        </summary>
                    </msContents>
